---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import EventSection from "../components/events/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="Felix Schneider">
    <EventSection />

    <section>
        <h2>The Art of Structural Engineering</h2>
        <p>
            At vero eos et accusamus et iusto odio dignissimos ducimus qui
            blanditiis praesentium voluptatum deleniti atque corrupti quos
            dolores et quas molestias excepturi sint occaecati cupiditate non
            provident, similique sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollitia
            animi.
        </p>
        <blockquote>
            "Simplicity is a great virtue but it requires hard work to achieve
            it and education to appreciate it. And to make things worse:
            complexity sells better."
        </blockquote>
    </section>

    <hr />

    <section>
        <h3>Core Principles & Technical Stack</h3>
        <p>
            Quis autem vel eum iure reprehenderit qui in ea voluptate velit esse
            quam nihil molestiae consequatur, vel illum qui dolorem eum fugiat
            quo voluptas nulla pariatur?
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Performance:</strong> Lightweight static compilation with
                minimal runtime.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Typography:</strong> Clear hierarchy using strict fluid type
                scales.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Aesthetics:</strong> High-contrast monochrome palettes with
                precise neon highlights.
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            For more updates on what I am hacking on, check out the <a
